cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.IR

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category as the paper deals with automated pavement distress detection using road images and deep learning models. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of deep learning frameworks for pavement distress classification. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper involves the development of an automated system for pavement condition assessment. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are less likely categories as they are not directly related to the topic of the paper.
